/blogs/news/new-music-release-castlevania-ii-simons-quest|title=New Music Release: CASTLEVANIA II: SIMON'S QUEST – Mondo|publisher=Mondo|access-date=2017-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170626192701/https://mondotees.com/blogs/news/new-music-release-castlevania-ii-simons-quest|archive-date=2017-06-26|url-status=live}}</ref> Some reviewers have praised Matsubara's compositions.<ref name="CV2History"/><ref name="IGNReview"/> [[GameSpy]] called all of the music "incredible", and one of the first appearances of "classics like 'The Silence of Daylight'".<ref name="CV2GameSpy">{{Cite web|url=http://castlevaniadungeon.net/games/cv2.html|title=Castlevania 2: Simon's Quest|publisher=ClassicGaming.com. [[GameSpy]]|access-date=2008-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110723035624/http://castlevaniadungeon.net/games/cv2.html|archive-date=2011-07-23|url-status=live}}</ref>

